name: Company/Organisation Logo
description:
Fancy a new custom logo for your company/organisation? 
Purchase this, then email me OllieGudgin@gmail.com with details on how you would like your logo (e.g. colours, theme, specific needs)

Design will take 2-3 Days for completion

For examples of my work, check out my online portfolio: http://olliearts.daportfolio.com/

**PLEASE NOTE**
For all my work, I will produce three different final designs, and then send you a watermarked preview version of each. You can then choose which design you ultimately want out of the three.
I take into consideration every detail you would like included.
